### Aggregation Example: Monthly Sales Summary

```javascript
const result = await Order.aggregate([
  { $match: { status: 'completed' } }, // Filter completed orders
  { $group: {
      _id: { month: { $month: "$createdAt" }, year: { $year: "$createdAt" } },
      totalSales: { $sum: "$amount" },
      count: { $sum: 1 }
